---
title: All-American Black Bean & Cheddar Burger with Potato Wedges & Sweet Chilli Aioli
description: We can bet you've never had a veggie burger quite like this before. With a cheesy black bean patty, soft, brioche-style buns and a
smear of sweet chilli aioli, plus potato wedges, this dish is a real treat.

